---
/* SECURITY: this old signup flow was live at /signup_full_BACKUP and
   created accounts without the Turnstile-verified edge function.
   Neutralized — a reference copy of the old code lives at the repo
   root (signup_full_BACKUP.astro), OUTSIDE src/pages, where it is
   not routed. Never keep backup pages inside src/pages. */
---
<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="robots" content="noindex, nofollow" />
    <meta http-equiv="refresh" content="0;url=/signup" />
    <link rel="canonical" href="/signup" />
    <title>Moved</title>
    <script is:inline>location.replace("/signup");</script>
  </head>
  <body>
    <p><a href="/signup">Continue to sign up</a></p>
  </body>
</html>
